<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Sabri Public High School</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/home.css">
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Navbar -->
    <header>
        <nav class="navbar">
            <div class="logo">
                <img id="img" src="/images/download.jpg" alt="School Logo">
                <h1 style="color:white; font-size:1.5em;">Sabri Public High School</h1>
            </div>
            <ul class="nav-links">
                <li><a href="#home">Home</a></li>
                <li><a href="admission.html">Admission</a></li>
                <li><a href="community.html">Community</a></li>
                <li><a href="#contact">Contact</a></li>
            </ul>
        </nav>
    </header>
    <!-- Home Section -->
    <section id="home" class="home">
        <h1>Welcome to <%=name%></h1>
        <p>Located in Chak 313 JB, our mission is to provide quality education and empower our students to achieve their dreams in a nurturing environment.</p>
        <a class="special-button" href="first.html">Get Started</a>
    </section>
    <section id="principal-message" class="message">
        <div class="message-container">
            <h2>Message from the Principal</h2>
            <p>
                Dear Parents,  
                At Sabri Public High School, we are dedicated to nurturing the leaders of tomorrow. Our mission is to provide a solid foundation of education that not only emphasizes academic excellence but also instills values of integrity, discipline, and compassion.  
                We recognize that education is a shared journey between the school and families, and together, we can ensure a brighter future for our students.
            </p>
            <p>
                We are committed to creating a supportive and challenging environment where every child can discover their unique potential and achieve greatness. As we move forward, I assure you that our focus will remain on developing well-rounded individuals who are equipped to excel academically and contribute positively to society.
            </p>
            <p>
                Thank you for entrusting us with your child's education. Let us work hand in hand to inspire and empower them to reach their highest aspirations.
            </p>
            <p style="text-align: right; font-style: italic; margin-top: 30px;">
                Yours sincerely,  
                <br>
                <strong>Surf Javed</strong>  
                <br>
                Principal, Sabri Public High School
            </p>
            <p style="text-align: right; margin-top: 10px; font-family: 'Dancing Script', cursive; font-size: 1.5em; color: #333;">
                Surf Javed
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>
    

    <!-- Contact Form Section -->
    <section id="contact" class="contact">
        <h2>Contact Us</h2>
        <form>
            <label for="name">Full Name</label>
            <input type="text" id="name" name="name" placeholder="Your Full Name" required>

            <label for="email">Email</label>
            <input type="email" id="email" name="email" placeholder="Your Email Address" required>

            <label for="message">Message</label>
            <textarea id="message" name="message" rows="5" placeholder="Your Message" required></textarea>

            <button type="submit">Send Message</button>
        </form>
    </section>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2024 Sabri Public High School, Chak 313 JB. All Rights Reserved.</p>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>